{"tid":1296766,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛中國，學文化] 月餅的由來","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:27:46.000Z","uid":49803,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1297ed3338bf4213b553f50cae9152133807a28d","tid":1296766,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"又就黎中秋節，巴絲們屋企都應該有買月餅啦！唔知大家又知唔知月餅點黎呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n月餅是中秋節的應節食品，也是團圓的象徵，如果一家人能在中秋節同吃月餅，便有一家團聚的意思了。原來，月餅還曾擔任過重要的歷史任務呢。<br />\n<br />\n相傳元朝時，蒙古人壓迫漢人。到了元朝末期，漢人奮起反抗。有一次，率領民眾反抗的主將朱元璋要將反抗的信息祕密傳到百姓手裏。於是他的軍師劉伯溫想出一條妙計，他裝扮成賣餅人，將紙條放進月餅內，上面寫著：「中秋夜，齊動手，殺撻子。」結果成功地把反元的信息祕密傳播開去。想不到，看似平凡的月餅卻曾擔任不平凡的任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkedcity.net/sch_files/a/phc/phc-cic/public_html/MoonCake.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkedcity.net%2Fsch_files%2Fa%2Fphc%2Fphc-cic%2Fpublic_html%2FMoonCake.htm&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpQuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=638cac0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkedcity.net/sch_files/a/phc/phc-cic/public_html/MoonCake.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c68a52ec86771382f703dec1c6a91a3d0848521d","tid":1296766,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"劉伯溫一定收咗人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab69d0dbabb7ea5b857a2ffc39b3a0df554eea9","tid":1296766,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"啲百姓咁易俾人煽動到，又唔關自己事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f547bace2287fd2b0ee20fe01a77cc466eadca0b","tid":1296766,"uid":109197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"中秋去邊賞月好？"},{"pid":"1c5d014a425d790cb538add8017e1c2561518797","tid":1296766,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f547bace2287fd2b0ee20fe01a77cc466eadca0b","tid":1296766,"uid":109197,"like":0,"dislike